# Title: Disable Windows Security Center Notifications
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-08-19
# Level: medium
# Description: Detect set UseActionCenterExperience to 0 to disable the Windows security center notification
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.defense-evasion, attack.t1112
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/registry/registry_set/registry_set_disable_security_center_notifications.yml

Details="DWORD (0x00000000)" TargetObject="*Windows\\CurrentVersion\\ImmersiveShell\\UseActionCenterExperience"